1: Download Timer Resolution_build 
2: Once downloaded, extract the zip file.
3: Now Left click on timerresolution.exe and open its propery
4: Now click on Compatibility Tab.
5: Tick on Run this program as an administrator and Apply the changes.
6: Now close the window and double-click on the TimerResolution.exe file.
7: The Timer Resolution tool window will open, displaying the current timer resolution settings.
8: To adjust the timer resolution, click on the “Maximum” button to set it to the highest value possible. This will ensure the timer resolution is as precise as possible.
